{"tid":504693,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)巨星夫婿","createTime":"2017-12-20T09:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T18:00:27.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dee172280ca40db3dcf5108101659e5b63bc02b2","tid":504693,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:43:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔曬下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=12907e7c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=84af33e5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=e9942878\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.4meee.com/files/article/757354/large_757354_1.jpg?23210900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.4meee.com%2Ffiles%2Farticle%2F757354%2Flarge_757354_1.jpg%3F23210900&h=646b4d47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n櫻庭裕一郎（長瀨智也飾演）是風靡全日本的年輕歌手，被選為「希望能被他擁抱No.1」的稱號，迷倒萬千少女&hellip;&hellip;但是這個當紅的大明星在現實生活中竟是一個滿口大阪腔、邋遢、老土的住家男人。<br />\n演出時裕一郎需要改變本身的形象迎合媒體和粉絲們的口味，讓自己身心俱疲，直到遇見了21歲的櫻子（竹內結子飾演），她從不把裕一郎當作公眾人物，兩人之間的自然相處總讓裕一郎如沐春風。因為裕一郎自少便失去父母，所以希望能與櫻子建立一個「世界上最溫暖的家」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f7413370\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=UxwceqvxZF8HMDpdtcTRI2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=417849cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b30f66314580f6c06943929135343c38c9ff0c","tid":504693,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e088bcf20c5749941e3c984e5ef385f43177568","tid":504693,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T09:58:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b20dc25c9b5284399593c95651adef1445af7e","tid":504693,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa435528d4a8f0c6d1b476ff75136c9c97a8c972","tid":504693,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r